2B50A2C0.Line7.EECAE: And thank the spirits you did, friend.

915C293E.Line5.EECAE: Overseer Kafan. One of the worst. He sent droves to an early grave. Myself included. But I got lucky--

C5451C42.Line9.EECAE: As for you. You helped not just us, but every soul of the Steppes that was trapped here by those relics. Coin is a poor payment for eternal rest, but I hope you’ll accept it anyway?

F767AFBC.Line3.EECAE: I saved you from that charnel pit. Not luck.
